node.text: Omg love wearing nightgown to work 💗

The next best thing to staying in bed on a rainy day — is wearing a nightgown to work. ⁣
⁣
Don't sleep on this trend. Women in NYC are co-opting frilled, long-sleeved nightgowns as everyday dresses. ⁣
⁣
While summer was once seen as the season to bare all, a celebratory moment to shed winter’s layers and reveal an unobstructed silhouette — the post #MeToo era has heralded a new modesty in some quarters of women’s fashion. ⁣
⁣
Tap the link in bio for more.
